name: Login Test Feature
description:
As a User
  I should be able to login successfully with valid credentials
  I should not be able to login with invalid credentials
  I should able to logout successfully
  I should see the logo on homepage

children.name: User should get error message with invalid credentials
User should get error message with invalid credentials
When User Enter Username "Admin"
And User Enter password "admin123"
And User click on login button
When User login to Application successfully
Then User should get error message "Required" depends on username "" and password ""
